title: Always show reset menu option in tablet
message:
Always show reset menu option in tablet

There is a bug in android that is preventing the reset from being shown whenset as hidden in xml.
This prevented the reset button from being shown after a sub region query, giveing the user no
means to reset the query.

Lets just show it all the time, resetting when already reset is a no-op

title: Offline map performance improvment
message:
Offline map performance improvment

Rather than add all offline map polygons when async task is finished, add them as the async task
progresses.
